            "clusion": "I",
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "Subjects fulfilling all of the following criteria will be included in the study:  o Female inmates on the lists provided by the detention institutions or male inmates randomly selected from the lists provided by the detention institutions.  o Aged 18 to 80 years.  o Freely given, informed consent form signed."
